fusion with <i>Ann(e)</i> in earlier centuries. Frequent in the medieval period, the name was revived in the 19th century, and has been especially popular in Scotland.  See also  Annis ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Agnes was born about 1285. She had at least 1 son with William Hillary."},"et":{"about 1285–":"umbes 1285–Surnud","1290–Male":"1290–Surnud","1305–1357":"1305–1357","1285–Female":"1285–Surnud","1305":"1305","1357":"1357","October 1305":"oktoober 1305","1285":"1285","about 1285":"umbes 1285","1290":"1290","Bescote, Staffordshire, England":"Bescot, Staffordshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"about 1285–":"noin 1285–Kuollut","1290–Male":"1290–Kuollut","1305–1357":"1305–1357","1285–Female":"1285–Kuollut","1305":"1305","1357":"1357","October 1305":"lokakuu 1305","1285":"1285","about 1285":"noin 1285","1290":"1290","Bescote, Staffordshire, England":"Bescot, Staffordshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"about 1285–":"environ 1285–Décédée","1290–Male":"1290–Décédé","1305–1357":"1305–1357","1285–Female":"1285–Décédée","1305":"1305","1357":"1357","October 1305":"octobre 1305","1285":"1285","about 1285":"environ 1285","1290":"1290","Bescote, Staffordshire, England":"Bescot, Staffordshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Agnes est née environ 1285. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec William Hillary."},"de":{"about 1285–":"um 1285–Verstorben","1290–Male":"1290–Verstorben","1305–1357":"1305–1357","1285–Female":"1285–Verstorben","1305":"1305","1357":"1357","October 1305":"Oktober 1305","1285":"1285","about 1285":"um 1285","1290":"1290","Bescote, Staffordshire, England":"Bescot, Staffordshire, England, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Agnes wurde um 1285 geboren. Sie hatte mit William Hillary mindestens 1 Sohn."},"ht":{"about 1285–":"about 1285–Desede","1290–Male":"1290–Desede","1305–1357":"1305–1357","1285–Female":"1285–Desede","1305":"1305","1357":"1357","October 1305":"October 1305","1285":"1285","about 1285":"about 1285","1290":"1290","Bescot